snippet.title: Mindkatt Trailer
snippet.description:
The current status of the game from alpha to beta.

Here begins the story of Mindkatt where you can play the first 3 levels of episode one.

From now on the game will update from this starting point.

At the beginning of the year 2025, all of episode 1 will be finished.

The re-evolution begins!
